-- Hong Kong Office Sells for Record $3,300 Per Square Foot, Standard Reports
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-11-08T20:24:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-08/hong-kong-office-sells-for-record-3-300-per-square-foot-standard-reports.html
A unit in the Center office building
in Hong Kong’s Central district sold for HK$25,581 ($3,300) per
square foot, setting a new record for the city, the Standard
said, citing Land Registry data.  The previous record, set last month, was HK$25,000 per
square foot for a unit in No. 9 Queen’s Road Central, the Hong
Kong-based English-language newspaper reported. The buyer in the
Center paid HK$338 million, the Standard said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  